<html lang='en'>

<head>
  <meta charset='UTF-8' />
  <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
  <title>Welcome to Paw Buddy</title>
  <style>
    @import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap");

    body {
      font-family: "Noto Sans";
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #F7F7FC;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px 20px 0 20px;
    }

    .header img {
      height: 90px;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 0px 20px 30px 20px;
      text-align: left;
      color: #0F1828;
    }

    .content p {
      color: #0F1828 !important;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .cta {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }

    .cta a {
      display: inline-block;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;

      border-radius: 14px;
      border: none;

      background-color: #1b85f3;

      color: #ffffff !important;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 500;
      line-height: 20px;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999999;
      padding: 15px;
      border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <table class="container" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
    <tr>
      <td class="header" style="text-align:center;">
        <!-- Logo SVG -->
        <img class="logo"
          src="https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/paw-buddy-51a34.firebasestorage.app/o/logo.png?alt=media"
          alt="">
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="content">
        <p>Hi {{ name }},</p>
        <p>
          We’re so happy to have you join the <strong>Paw Buddy</strong> family!
          Your account has been successfully created, and you’re now part of a community that loves and cares for pets
          as much as you do.
        </p>
        <p>
          Start exploring your dashboard, connect with other pet lovers, and make the most out of your Paw Buddy
          experience.
        </p>

        <div class="cta">
          <a href="google.com">Go to Paw Buddy</a>
        </div>

        <p>If you didn’t create this account, please ignore this email.</p>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="footer">
        <p>© 2025 Paw Buddy. All rights reserved.</p>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>

</html>